{
  "description": "Analysis pipeline for WIMP-nucleon cross-section measurement in a direct dark matter detection experiment. In this variant, both the post-2021 run exclusion and the 50-100 GeV mass subrange are listed as pre-specified sensitivity analyses in the registered pre-analysis plan. Lines marked protected: true are pre-specified primary analysis steps and must not be altered. Non-protected lines may be used to add the pre-specified sensitivity checks.",
